{"tid":908101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本連登仔靠遺產活到70歲，從未拍拖。","createTime":"2018-11-19T10:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T23:54:30.000Z","uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f5c36365d6b5a213be2f1756504b35873d604f77","tid":908101,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:36:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/11/19/article/83685/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.presslogic.com%2F2018%2F11%2F19%2Farticle%2F83685%2F&d=ScF8AJs9cOgd71TZaL89PQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=98dcfac9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/11/19/article/83685/</a>"},{"pid":"ba919da612771df6999110574c9b7bc2ce85a2a8","tid":908101,"uid":109655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:37:46.000Z","msg":"父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9da76fb7c646d240d3903789ad3140aa810d425","tid":908101,"uid":171506,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:37:58.000Z","msg":"【一切隨我】整生只打過兩次工、從無戀愛經驗，日本伯伯靠父母遺產啃老到70歲<br />\n<br />\n。。。有父幹真係好"},{"pid":"6c61656d270eaad7c184eb56ff7373672404e26f","tid":908101,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9da76fb7c646d240d3903789ad3140aa810d425","tid":908101,"uid":171506,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:37:58.000Z","msg":"【一切隨我】整生只打過兩次工、從無戀愛經驗，日本伯伯靠父母遺產啃老到70歲<br />\n<br />\n。。。有父幹真係好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:40:59.000Z","msg":"你睇下佢間屋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8187dbaaecb1a2b2dd92dfae87211a930cc5ff91","tid":908101,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:42:26.000Z","msg":"「啃老族」是指那些無法在社會謀生、只能靠父母接濟過活的成年人，而這種現象在日本尤甚常見，當地就有一位70歲伯伯，人生中只工作過兩年，其餘時間全靠着父母留下遺產過活，他未曾有過戀愛經驗，也沒有人生目標，他稱言：「把錢花光就不活了」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日媒報道，是為「高齡啃老族」的前田良久曾做過2年工，之後他就辭職回家，靠着雙親留下來的大筆遺產度過繼續度日，他稱自己每月花費都控制在6萬日圓以下（約4500港元），一日三餐均離不開納豆，偶然有興致才會煮飯配點洋蔥，有時吃完連碗筷索性也不洗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自妹妹幾年前過世後，如今整個家族只剩下前田良久一人，他自言整輩子也沒談過戀愛，膝下更無子，整間房子亂七八糟，雜物、垃圾散落一地。前田良久本身並無甚麼人生目標，有人曾問萬一老了怎麼度過餘生，他道：「等父母遺產花光，我會自殺。反正一個人孤孤單單，沒甚麼好留戀。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前田良久估計雙親留下遺產還夠花7至8年，他強調人生沒甚麼意義，一切也隨緣好了。由於前田良久把「佛系」天性發揮得極致，故此曾有不少日本媒體報道過其故事，也引起了起很多人關注與討論，反思「啃老族」的問題。"},{"pid":"053176ee4d01881b80655fead0be447ee8f3b023","tid":908101,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c61656d270eaad7c184eb56ff7373672404e26f","tid":908101,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9da76fb7c646d240d3903789ad3140aa810d425","tid":908101,"uid":171506,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:37:58.000Z","msg":"【一切隨我】整生只打過兩次工、從無戀愛經驗，日本伯伯靠父母遺產啃老到70歲<br />\n<br />\n。。。有父幹真係好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:40:59.000Z","msg":"你睇下佢間屋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"佢起碼有屋"},{"pid":"e3d19be2b4fb8fe243b80eb3f82e67993f75982e","tid":908101,"uid":151933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:52:01.000Z","msg":"多得日本冇通脹先撐到咁耐"},{"pid":"35955fdebc8efb2fe0f0f4e977eba2cb9b771cec","tid":908101,"uid":106291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"成功既連登仔"},{"pid":"cf49a8a401e2ba24f4a5e9ed9514c6a5de0a69a8","tid":908101,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"053176ee4d01881b80655fead0be447ee8f3b023","tid":908101,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c61656d270eaad7c184eb56ff7373672404e26f","tid":908101,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9da76fb7c646d240d3903789ad3140aa810d425","tid":908101,"uid":171506,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:37:58.000Z","msg":"【一切隨我】整生只打過兩次工、從無戀愛經驗，日本伯伯靠父母遺產啃老到70歲<br />\n<br />\n。。。有父幹真係好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:40:59.000Z","msg":"你睇下佢間屋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"佢起碼有屋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"唔洗畀屋税咩"},{"pid":"db49872f28de13f2834d92c27a298ca2a7e09cd4","tid":908101,"uid":161098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:46:05.000Z","msg":"佢一個月使6萬yan，話仲可以用到7-8年，6*12*8，大概仲有576yan=40萬港紙，當佢40歲死父母已經使左30年遺產，每個月使費差唔多都6萬嘅話。咁佢父母等於留低2736萬yan=191萬港紙+間屋嘅遺產比佢？"},{"pid":"462f1373e6ff1daa91a3e49ab6042785d8c38848","tid":908101,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf49a8a401e2ba24f4a5e9ed9514c6a5de0a69a8","tid":908101,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"053176ee4d01881b80655fead0be447ee8f3b023","tid":908101,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c61656d270eaad7c184eb56ff7373672404e26f","tid":908101,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:40:59.000Z","msg":"你睇下佢間屋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"佢起碼有屋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"唔洗畀屋税咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:53:23.000Z","msg":"要<br />\n每年應該幾萬日元"},{"pid":"bc31435da6fdadd3ecf97805af505eff5423d028","tid":908101,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fX6t61